1-xpclr_convert_rho_to_cM.R
Use R script to convert recombination rate estimates from Ldhelmet to centi-Morgan (cM) for P.tremula

1-interpolate_map_to_snp.R
Use R script to interpolate genetic distance between adjacent SNPs according to the centimorgan values

1-xpclr.aspen_species.rec_cM.sh
pipeline to run XPCLR

1-Figure5.R
R script to plot the Figure5

1-manhanttan_plot.R
Function to make the manhanttan plot

2-betascan.sh
Script to run BetaScan analysis

2-Figure6.R
R script to plot the Figure6
